      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Yea also, when he that is a fool walketh by the way",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The general drift of the proverb seems plain enough. “",
        "children": []
