      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "fails him, and he manifests his folly",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".” The last clause, however, admits of two constructions, each of which has the support of high authorities, (1) ",
        "children": []
      },
