        "text": "Romans 12:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). On the whole the latter construction seems preferable. So it is notoriously the most significant symptom of insanity that the patient looks on all others as insane. It may be noted that (1) finds a parallel in ",
